    "body": "This is a PR that adds high-order interpolation/reconstruction for the vertical flux on staggered 1D grids. \r\n\r\nA word of caution: Currently, we need to figure out the boundary conditions, so it supports only periodic meshes and, therefore, it's tested only on a periodic domain.\r\n\r\nOn periodic domains, for a constant velocity field, it does exhibit the desired order of convergence: 3. \r\n \r\n This will close #524 \r\n",
